      "title": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Hanuman World Luge"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Get ready for an action-packed adventure in Hanuman World Phuket. Glide through 16 ziplines along with rappel lines, sky bridges, and spiral cases featured in the eco park. Witness panoramic views as you fly through lush canopies. Thrillseekers may opt for the intense roller zipline, which runs at a high speed through the entire park. Admire the local flora and fauna from the sky walk. Then, unwind on the trampoline-like sun bed and fruit and juice bar. Journey to Phuket for an exhilarating ziplining adventure!"
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.3,
        "rating_count": 100
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "With multiple ziplines of varying lengths and heights, adventurers can choose their own level of challenge and excitement."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Embark on a heart-pounding zipline journey through the treetops of Phuket's pristine rainforest."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "In addition to ziplines, Hanuman World Phuket features sky bridges that traverse the canopy, offering a unique perspective of the jungle below."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Immerse yourself in the natural beauty of Phuket's rainforest as you zip through the trees."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Hanuman World Phuket is an exhilarating adventure park nestled in the lush jungles of Phuket, Thailand."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Hanuman World gives you a slice of the time when the Monkey God showed that he had no limits, feared nothing, and would do everything to reach his goal. Just like a dedicated adventurer should. So whether you are an adrenaline junkie or a nature lover, or even someone seeking a unique and unforgettable experience, Hanuman World Phuket adventure zipline park is your must-visit destination. Let the thrilling zip-line adventure through the lush greenery of Phuket be your next unforgettable journey! Additionally, we also have our first Zipline Park named Flying Hanuman which is purely located next to the waterfall in Kathu,Phuket."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
